# Apple Maps

- Website: https://maps.apple.com
- Open Source: No
- Privacy Focused: Better than Google

## Why Use It?

Apple Maps focuses more on privacy compared to many mainstream alternatives.

### Unique Benefits

- Better privacy than Google Maps
- Deep Apple ecosystem integration
- Clean interface
- Strong navigation features
- Look Around street imagery

### Best For

Apple users wanting a privacy-friendlier mainstream option.

---

# Google Maps

- Website: https://maps.google.com
- Open Source: No
- Privacy Focused: Low

## Why Mention It?

Google Maps remains extremely popular because of its large dataset and business information.

### Downsides

- Extensive location tracking
- Data collection concerns
- Reliance on Google ecosystem
- Privacy tradeoffs

### Best Alternative Replacements

- Organic Maps
- OsmAnd
- Magic Earth
- OpenStreetMap apps

---

# Waze

- Website: https://waze.com
- Open Source: No
- Privacy Focused: Low

## Why Mention It?

Waze is known for real-time traffic reporting and route optimization.

### Downsides

- Owned by Google
- Heavy data collection
- Location tracking concerns

### Best Alternative Replacements

- Magic Earth
- HERE WeGo
- Organic Maps

