# Final Thoughts

Navigation apps often collect massive amounts of location data.  
Choosing a better maps platform can improve:

- Privacy
- Battery life
- Offline access
- Data ownership
- Independence from Big Tech ecosystems

Whenever possible, support open geographic projects like OpenStreetMap that keep mapping data free and community-driven.
